---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const lastUpdated = "March 2026";
---

<BaseLayout title="T.N. Hamilton | Now">
    <article class="mt-16 mb-24">
        <header class="mb-12">
            <h1
                class="text-4xl font-semibold mb-2 tracking-tight text-zinc-100"
            >
                Now
            </h1>
            <p class="text-sm font-mono text-gold/60 uppercase tracking-widest">
                Last Updated: {lastUpdated}
            </p>
        </header>

        <div class="space-y-16">
            <section>
                <h2
                    class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-gold font-bold mb-6 border-b border-zinc-800 pb-2"
                >
                    Professional & Academic
                </h2>
                <ul class="space-y-4 text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
                    <li>
                        <span class="text-zinc-200">Focus:</span> I'm currently working
                        on making my personal site using the Astro 6. I've put this
                        off for a while but decided to start on it due to my recent
                        commits from my Linux config.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="text-zinc-200">Studying:</span> I'm currently
                        taking many courses regarding U.S. politics, global sociology,
                        and Cybersecurity policy. I've found that these courses overlap
                        in many discussion points which has led me to shape how I
                        view the actions taken by nation states – especially those
                        involving cyber.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2
                    class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-gold font-bold mb-6 border-b border-zinc-800 pb-2"
                >
                    Personal Hobbies
                </h2>
                <ul class="space-y-4 text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
                    <li>
                        <span class="text-zinc-200">Currently Reading:</span> I'm
                        currently reading
                        <span class="italic">Fear and Trembling</span> by Soren Kierkegaard.
                        After completing a philosophy course, I was inspired to read
                        further into how philosophers argue the existence of God or
                        a higher, more supernatural power. This book is just the first
                        in my library on this topic.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="text-zinc-200">Hobby:</span> I've taken on a
                        more senior role in USAFA's Cyber Team, Delogrand, this semester.
                        As a result, I am now constructing CTF-style competitions
                        to assist in training and development of both Red and Blue
                        skills. Ultimately, I've learned a lot about system architecture,
                        patching, and system misconfigurations.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </section>
        </div>
    </article>
</BaseLayout>
